These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, animation, spy, martial-arts
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, train, bus, subway
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the train and the person driving the bus##2
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | zombie     | spy | animation |
| Transport     | skateboard     | bus | subway  | train      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, blues, indie, pop
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, airplane, taxi, skateboard
1. the fan of blues is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of pop is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | house | blues    | pop     | indie  |
| Transport     | bike    | taxi | airplane | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, gospel, indie, trance
4 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, goldfish, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
2. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the fan of trance##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | indie   | blues  | trance |
| Pet           | frog | pony | goldfish | ferret  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, traveling, hiking, photography
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, japanese, russian, german
1. the german is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the russian##2
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the russian is on the left or right of the german##3
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the pakistani is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | traveling | cooking | photography | hiking  |
| Nationality   | japanese  | pakistani   | german  | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, mirinda, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, video-games, chess, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | sprite    | juice   | mirinda | milk    |
| Hobby      | video-games | photography | chess       | traveling |

