.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, mirinda, iced-tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, taxi, bike, jet-ski
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person drinking mirinda##2
3. the person driving the car is between the person driving the bike and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | 7up | mirinda | iced-tea | sprite |
| Transport   | taxi | car  | bike    | jet-ski  |

