3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the german is between the dutch and the british##2
5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the skateboard and the british##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | brazilian | british | german | dutch     |
| Transport     | boat | quad-bike  | jet-ski   | skateboard |

