.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, reading, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, disaster, time-travel, romance
1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | reading | camping | card-games   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | time-travel | satire      | romance |

