.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, rat, rabbit, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, sailing, lacrosse, weightlifting
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the rat is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | bird | rat   | rabbit      | mouse      |
| Sport   | sailing     | lacrosse | ice-hockey | weightlifting |

