.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, british, french, pakistani
4 different pets are kept: pony, chinchilla, turtle, hedgehog
1. the british is on the far right##1
2. the mexican is the mexican##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
4. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the british##3
5. the french is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | mexican | french  | pakistani | british |
| Pet           | turtle     | hedgehog | pony    | chinchilla     |

