4. the freelancer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating peach is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | kale  | banana | eggplant  | peach      |
| Job    | designer | lawyer | project-manager | freelancer |

