3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of disco is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
6. the fan of gospel is the person who's hobby is chess##1
7. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | puzzles | video-games | fishing | chess |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | electronic       | disco   | gospel      |

