.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, lemonade, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, house, hip-hop, classical
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
4. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of rock##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    | iced-tea  | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | house | hip-hop | classical  |

