4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rat, rabbit, goat
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is the owner of the goat##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
4. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the person watching action movies and the owner of the goat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | time-travel  | adventure  | action |
| Pet           | goldfish    | goat | rabbit | rat |

