2. the writer is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
3. the teacher is on the left of the person eating peach##1
4. the social-worker is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
5. the social-worker is on the left of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | grapes        | nectarine       | lettuce   | peach |
| Job    | writer | social-worker | teacher | bartender  |

